snippet.title: The HD Adventures of Rotating Octopus Character - PS Vita - Trailer
snippet.description:
he HD Adventures of Rotating Octopus Character is a vibrant, joyful remaster of the popular PSP™ game. Recreated in high-definition with PlayStation®Vita exclusive features, this is the definitive version of one of 2011's highest rated PSP™ games.

Vita exclusive features: Trophies, Leaderboards, beautiful new HD graphics and balance tuning.
